      <text xml:space="preserve">{{wiktionary|car}}
A '''[[car]]''', or automobile, motor car, is a wheeled motor vehicle used for transporting passengers.

'''Car''' or '''CAR''' may also refer to:
{{TOC right}}
==Transportation==
===Vehicles===
* [[Railroad car]], a vehicle on a train that is towed by the locomotive
* The cab of an [[elevator]]
* A vehicle on a [[tram]] (trolley)
* [[Chariot]], an archaic term
* [[Carriage]], an archaic term
* [[Cart]], an archaic term

==Media and entertainment==
