==Standards==
{{Main|Institut d'Estudis Catalans|Acadèmia Valenciana de la Llengua}}
{| class=&quot;infobox bordered&quot; cellpadding=&quot;4&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;width:250px; font-size:95%; float:right; float:right;&quot;
