Computer [[programmer]]s are those who write computer software. Their jobs usually involve:
*[[Source code|Coding]]
*[[Compiler|Compilation]]
*[[Debugging]]
*[[Documentation]]
*[[Digital integration|Integration]]
*[[Software maintenance|Maintenance]]
*[[Requirements analysis]]
*[[Software architecture]]
*[[Software testing]]
*[[Specification]]

